data.description:
Charming 1,721 square foot home located in Yukon with 4 spacious bedrooms, or an option of 3 bedrooms and a dedicated office/study, perfect for those who work from home or need a quiet space for creativity.
As you step inside, you are greeted by a warm and inviting living area, complete with a cozy fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxation or entertaining guests. The kitchen has plenty of counter and cabinet space, plus a convenient breakfast bar for casual dining.  The main bedroom is a true retreat, offering ample space and an ensuite full bath that's a sanctuary of its own, featuring a whirlpool tub for those relaxing soaks, a separate shower, and an Australian closet, providing abundant storage space.  The outdoor amenities are equally impressive. The backyard backs up to a serene greenbelt and includes an above-ground pool, covered patio, and a large deck. A storage building is also included, offering additional space for your needs.  This home is more than just a place to live; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful house your new home.
